Package smile.data

Interface DataFrame

All Superinterfaces:
Dataset<Tuple>, Iterable<BaseVector>
All Known Implementing Classes:
IndexDataFrame
public interface DataFrame extends Dataset<Tuple>, Iterable<BaseVector>
An immutable collection of data organized into named columns.
